Life.name: LA DOUBLEJ
Life.description: Wildbird set of 6 dessert plates
Life.details: Designed by La DoubleJ in collaboration with Italian ceramic giants Ancap, the colorful Wildbird dessert plate set is a selection of fine porcelain plates defined by bold patterns and hand-painted gold trims. Dishwasher safe, this colorful set of six plates is equally suited to serving salads and can be paired with other plates by La DoubleJ for a maximalist explosion of pattern and pigment.
